data.description:
Welcome to this multi-family residence, offering a convenient and vibrant lifestyle close to downtown Missoula. This property features three separate residences, providing an excellent investment opportunity or a chance to live in one unit while renting out the others. With a main level comprising a spacious 2-bedroom, 1-bathroom living space, and a lower level offering a studio and a 1-bedroom living, this property provides versatile options for residents. The convenience of shared laundry facilities is on the lower level for all residents. Outside, the level lot is fully fenced yard and offers space for outdoor activities, gardening, or enjoying the fresh Montana air. NEW ROOF was recently installed. Additionally, a new section of the sewer line has been replaced.
The location of this multi-family residence is truly unbeatable. Situated close to downtown Missoula, residents can enjoy easy access to free public transportation, an array of amenities including shopping, dining, entertainment, and other attractions. The University of Montana, parks, hiking trails, and the Clark Fork River are all within close proximity, providing opportunities for outdoor recreation and leisure. Whether you're an investor looking for a rental property or a homeowner seeking the benefits of additional rental income, this property offers endless potential. Contact Jen Clement at 406.360.9849 or your real estate professional.
